_sText:
Map was inspired by mg_buttons_roulette by Paul_Deagle, but i created my own concept and design, also i got to r4p3 source engine(jk ofc XD) in order to get kills from crusher to T player.

The T objective is to use buttons that control crushers and kill cts
The CT objective is to survive 4 minutes, then glass will break and T will become reachable.

Report any bugs immidately.
